 	together with AC_CHECK_LIB because that has its own caching.  Set
 	INTLLIBS=-lintl if gettext() and bindtextdomain() are in -lintl.
 	Use $INTLLIBS when checking for dcgettext() and _nl_msg_cat_cntr.
